properties.Name: PaymentCardStatusType
properties.Description:
A type of status that may be associated with a  Payment Card for a period of time.

Ex:
- Active
- Current
- Dormant
- Blocked
- Frozen
- Suspended
- Delinquent
- In Default
- Unknown
